'''Olivia "Mousy" McCallum''' is the daughter of [[Rick McCallum]], producer of the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[prequel trilogy]].

Mousy was a set production assistant for {{Film|III}} and played [[Padawan]] [[Bene]] in the film.<ref name="III" />

